<dl id="n06053h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06053h">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06053h"> 53(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> HCE hides in sand</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Un de mes divertissements d&apos;enfance, dit Ch&acirc;teaubriand, &ldquo;c&apos;&eacute;tait de construire, avec l&apos;ar&egrave;ne de la plage, des monuments, que mes camarades appelaient des <i>fours</i>&rdquo; <font color="green">[One of my childhood entertainments, said Chateaubriand, was to build, with the arena of the beach, monuments, which my comrades called furnaces]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 113?</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
